<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blood Bank</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Baloo Bhai 2', cursive;
            background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);
        }

        h1 {
            border: 2px solid grey;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: orangered;
        }

        section {
            border: 2px solid grey;
            width: 85%;
            margin: 40px auto;
            height: 450px;
            background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            animation: slide 10s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes slide {

            25% {
                background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
            }

            50% {
                background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
            }

            75% {
                background-image: url("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSg6_rz_fPq9g63FPy8TpsxPiPaoIGDoEgidw&usqp=CAU");
            }

            100% {
                background-image: url("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQqQqqvz4g28gdJBJC36fRsH8eeR3lCLfSV6g&usqp=CAU");
            }

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Blood Bank</h1>

    <section>

    </section>

</html>
